Where: Geyikbayırı, &lt;a href="https://www.flyinggoat.camp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Flying Goat Camp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Sector: &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/12562339" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Mağara&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/280294815" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Anatolia&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/3189478311" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Koridor&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/12562843" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Trebena East&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/12562843" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Trebena West&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/399677484" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Rüzgarlı Bahçe&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.thecrag.com/en/climbing/turkey/geyikbayiri/area/1038524988" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Küllüin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Grades: 6a+ to 6c+ (7a)&lt;/p&gt;
